h\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Featured&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Featured","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/featured\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":389,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/01\/18\/no-mercy-unless-show-mercy\/","url_meta":{"origin":597,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Mercy: Allah is not merciful to the unmerciful","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 18, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Jarir ibn 'Abdillah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Allah will not be merciful to those who are not merciful to people.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7376, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2319 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/09\/11\/rahmah-compassion-for-children\/","url_meta":{"origin":597,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Mercy: The Prophet is merciful to his children","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 11, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: Al-Aqra' ibn Habis saw the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, kissing his grandson Al-Hasan. He said, \u201cI have ten children and I do not kiss any of them.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, whoever does not show mercy will not receive 